## Development

### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/llamasearchai/llama-voice.git
cd llama-voice

# Install in editable mode with development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Testing

```bash
pytest tests/
```

